        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">This is to keep people from regenning mana the same way you can bandage past 50% at any level through creative swapping of items.</P><P>To explain both:<BR>Say I had base 1000 mana. 500 of that mana came from items. I go OOM, remove all my items, and put them all back on.. giving me 500 mana. This would be incredibly overpowering.. and would give me personally maybe 20 seconds of downtime.</P><P>To bandage past 50%, take off your hp items. Say you have 1000 hp, and you have a 100hp ring. Take off the 100hp ring, giving you 900hp. Bandage to 450 (50%) and then put the ring back on, giving you 550hp.</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Euri on 12/24/2001  01:02:19<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
